OL,5, A serving Metropolitan Police officer  
OL,6, has been sentenced for stalking a woman
OL,7, he met on duty.                        
OL,9,FPC Jonathan Simon, 44 received a       
OL,10,Fsuspended 16-week sentence for         
OL,11,Fharassing the woman after a break-up.  
OL,13,FHe was found guilty last month after   
OL,14,FWestminster Magistrates' Court heard he
OL,15,Frepeatedly visited her home, sometimes 
OL,16,Fwhile on duty, and left her messages   
OL,17,Fand voicemails.                        
OL,19,FThe judge said his behaviour had       
OL,20,Fbrought the Met Police into disrepute. 
